'''邁克爾·布萊恩·莫里森'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael Brian Morrison'''}}，{{bd|1988年|3月3日|catidx=Morrison, Michael}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，主要擔任[[後衛_(足球)|後衛]]，亦可以擔任[[右後衛|右後衛]]。現效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]。

==職業生涯==

===剑桥联===
莫里森在[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|剑桥联]]青年學院展開足球生涯，15歲時便入選預備隊名單，成為球隊史上最年輕的預備隊球員<ref name="Michael Morrison profile">{{cite web |url=http://www.cambridge-united.premiumtv.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10423~34393,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217024130/http://www.cambridge-united.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10423~34393,00.html |archivedate=2012-02-17|title=Michael Morrison profile |publisher=Cambridge United F.C. |quote=This towering centre-half played for the reserves at the age of 15 while still a schoolboy and became the youngest-ever Cambridge United player to do so. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2005年10月對[[哈利法克斯足球會|哈利法克斯]]的賽事，年僅17歲的莫里森在首次替一隊上場<ref name=sb0506>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=41763&season_id=135 |title=Games played by Michael Morrison in 2005/2006 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=23 November 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202105859/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=41763&season_id=135 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並2006年至2008年間連續三年當選為最佳年輕球員<ref name="Morrison makes Foxes move">{{cite news| url=http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=51038 |title=Morrison makes Foxes move |publisher=Non League Daily|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919105353/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=51038 |archivedate=19 September 2011 |quote=The fee for Morrison, who has been voted Cambridge's young player of the year for the past three years, also includes additional payments for appearances and a sell-on clause.}}</ref>。

===莱斯特城===
2008年7月2日，邁克爾·莫里森轉投[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]並簽約兩年，轉會費沒透露<ref name="Morrison moves To Walkers">{{cite web |url=http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1336492,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301230528/http://www.lcfc.com/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1336492,00.html |archivedate=2012-03-01|title=Morrison Moves To Walkers |publisher=Leicester City F.C. |date=2 July 2008 |accessdate=29 October 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。莫里森認為是次轉會對剑桥联十分有利，因為他可能約滿自由轉會使剑桥联人財兩失<ref name="Morrison pleased with Foxes move">{{cite news|title = Morrison pleased with Foxes move|url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7485857.stm|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 2 July 2008|accessdate = 29 October 2013|archive-date = 2019-08-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827031315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7485857.stm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。由於主教練[[尼格尔·皮尔逊|尼格尔·皮尔逊]]在球員時代司職後衛，因此莫里森視他為導師<ref name="Pearson can be mentor - Morrison">{{cite news|title = Pearson can be mentor – Morrison|url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7522911.stm|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 24 July 2008|accessdate = 29 October 2013|archive-date = 2019-08-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190824073605/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7522911.stm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。莫里森在8月9日對[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米尔顿凯恩斯]]的賽事首次上場，以2-0取勝<ref name="Leicester 2-0 MK Dons">{{cite news| title = Leicester 2–0 MK Dons| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541043.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 9 August 2008| accessdate = 9 August 2008| archive-date = 2017-08-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170827134339/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541043.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>，並在2009年1月24日對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]賽事打進在新球會的首顆入球<ref name="Leicester 4-2 Huddersfield">{{cite news| title = Leicester 4–2 Huddersfield| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7842905.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 24 January 2009| accessdate = 25 January 2009| archive-date = 2019-08-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190829020507/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7842905.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2008年11月，由於[[帕特里克·基斯諾伯|帕特里克·基斯諾伯]]受傷，使莫里森重返先發陣容<ref name="Morrison relishes first-team spot">{{cite news|title = Morrison relishes first-team spot|url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7725109.stm|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 12 November 2008|accessdate = 29 October 2013|archive-date = 2019-08-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827151209/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7725109.stm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。莫里森助球會贏得英甲冠軍，取得來季征戰英冠的資格，他並在主場最後一場賽事打進兩球，以2-2戰平[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯坎索普联]]<ref name="Leicester 2-2 Scunthorpe">{{cite news| title = Leicester 2–2 Scunthorpe| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8002063.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 24 April 2009| accessdate = 25 April 2009| archive-date = 2019-08-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190824033819/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8002063.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2009/10球季，莫里森的球衣號碼由15號改為4號<ref name="Morrison signs new Foxes contract">{{cite news| title=Morrison signs new Foxes contract| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8293037.stm| publisher=BBC Sport| date=6 October 2009| accessdate=29 October 2013| archive-date=2019-12-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214131014/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8293037.stm| dead-url=no}}</ref>，並努力爭取入選先發陣容<ref name="Morrison happy to fight for place">{{cite news|title = Morrison happy to fight for place|url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8138194.stm|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 7 July 2009|accessdate = 29 October 2013|archive-date = 2019-08-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190828212833/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8138194.stm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2009年10月6日，他與球會續約兩年至2012年<ref name="Morrison signs new Foxes contract">{{cite news| title=Morrison signs new Foxes contract| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8293037.stm| publisher=BBC Sport| date=6 October 2009| accessdate=29 October 2013}}</ref>。2009年12月26日對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]賽事中打進新球季的首顆進球，助球隊以2-1取勝<ref name="Leicester City too reliant on Matt Fryatt - Morrison">{{cite news|title = Leicester City too reliant on Matt Fryatt – Morrison|url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8434834.stm|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 30 December 2009|accessdate = 29 October 2013|archive-date = 2019-08-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190819105816/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8434834.stm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。由於隊友[[羅比·尼爾森|羅比·尼爾森]]表現不濟，莫里森在2010年1月改為出任右邊衛<ref name="Injury-hit Bruno Berner misses Leicester City's match at Swansea">{{cite news|title = Injury-hit Bruno Berner misses Leicester City's match at Swansea|url = http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/Injury-hit-Bruno-Berner-misses-Leicester-City-s-match-Swansea/story-12050752-detail/story.html|newspaper = Leicester Mercury|date = 16 January 2010|accessdate = 29 October 2013|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://archive.is/20131030094833/http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/Injury-hit-Bruno-Berner-misses-Leicester-City-s-match-Swansea/story-12050752-detail/story.html|archivedate = 2013年10月30日}}</ref>。

===谢周三===
2011年1月7日，莫里森與[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]簽約三年半<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.swfc.co.uk/page/News/0,,10304~2260609,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329034935/http://www.swfc.co.uk/page/News/0,,10304~2260609,00.html |archivedate=2012-03-29|title=Morrison capture complete |publisher=Sheffield Wednesday F.C. |date=7 January 2011 |accessdate=29 October 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===查尔顿竞技===
2011年7月12日，莫里森加盟英甲球會[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿竞技]]，簽約三年.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cafc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10267~2388963,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910070844/http://www.cafc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10267~2388963,00.html |archivedate=2011-09-10|title=Addicks move for Morrison |publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C. |date=12 July 2011 |accessdate=29 October 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。他很快成為了球隊的主力球員，並當選為2011年11月英甲每月最佳球員。2012/13球季，莫里森成為了球隊副隊長和主力後衛，並助球隊以第9名完成英冠聯賽。2014年6月24日，他與球會簽下兩年新約至2016年<ref>{{Cite web |title=Michael Morrison signs new contract |url=http://www.cafc.co.uk/news/article/20140624-morrison-contract-1668483.aspx |publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C. |date=24 June 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626032729/http://www.cafc.co.uk/news/article/20140624-morrison-contract-1668483.aspx |archivedate=2014年6月26日 }}</ref>。

===伯明翰===
2014年10月31日，莫里森外借至[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]兩個月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29848741 |title=Michael Morrison: Birmingham City sign Charlton defender on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=31 October 2014 |accessdate=31 October 2014 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604003038/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29848741 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。翌日對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的賽事便先發上場，最終0-0悶和<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29767126 |title=Wolves 0–0 Birmingham |publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 November 2014 |accessdate=1 November 2014 |archive-date=2015-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429013655/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29767126 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此後他保住先發位置，與隊長[[保羅·羅賓遜_(1978年出生後衛)|保羅·羅賓遜]]組成一對中後衛組合。同年12月，球會宣佈莫里森在1月永久加盟伯明翰城，簽約三年半<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/transfer/news/12691/9608942/sky-bet-championship-birmingham-reach-agreement-to-sign-defender-michael-morrison |title=Sky Bet Championship: Birmingham reach agreement to sign defender Michael Morrison |publisher=Sky Sports |date=16 December 2014 |accessdate=17 December 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202121438/https://www.skysports.com/transfer/news/12691/9608942/sky-bet-championship-birmingham-reach-agreement-to-sign-defender-michael-morrison |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該轉會在2015年1月5日正式完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/michael-morrison-birmingham-city-2179473.aspx |title=Morrison signs on the dotted line |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=5 January 2015 |accessdate=5 January 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105175527/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/michael-morrison-birmingham-city-2179473.aspx |archivedate=2015年1月5日 }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
莫里森在效力剑桥联期間，曾代表[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]上場參與[[2007-09年國際挑戰盃|2007-09年國際挑戰盃]]及[[四國錦標賽|四國錦標賽]]，並在後在賽事贏得冠軍<ref name="Comfortable win for Fairclough's boys">{{cite news| url=http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=46313|title=Comfortable win for Fairclough's boys|date=15 November 2007|publisher=Non League Daily |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060408/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=46313 |archivedate=21 September 2013}}</ref><ref name="Joy for Fairclough's boys">{{cite news| url=http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=50220|title=Joy for Fairclough's boys|date=25 May 2008|publisher=Non League Daily |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060638/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=50220 |archivedate=21 September 2013}}</ref>。

